data.description: Spacious, Inviting Single-Story Home with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and Covered Patio leading to your quaint backyard in The Royal Ridge Neighborhood encompassing the Royal Ridge Recreational Club. The Open Floor Plan boasts the perfect floor plan  and high ceilings. Large kitchen with breakfast bar and plenty of storage. Enormous living room is great for entertaining as it opens to the kitchen area, which leads to the covered patio. Master Suite is huge and includes a large walk-in closet, and private bathroom features dual vanity sinks, garden tub plus a separate shower, and commode in independent room. Very well-maintained home with gorgeous shade trees and a sprinkler system in the front yard. Numerous major repairs or upgrades including a new roof and gutters (2023), foundation repair with lifetime warranty (2022), new HVAC system (2017), water heater (2023), built-in microwave (2022), soft water (2021), garage door (2020), front door, many new blinds, etc. Tons of attic storage via pull-down stairs. Convenient Location is the understatement. Close to about everything you need, near City of Windcrest, quick access to 2 Interstate Freeways, major arteries, Ft Sam Military Base, SAMCC Medical Base, Randolph AFB
